    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事开始是发生在一个平凡的早晨，你如同平常抵达公司，发现居然所有同事都以为你要离职，觉得你是公司的叛徒，对你群起围攻，为了搞清楚发生什么事，你踏上了用 公事包保护自己的战斗之旅，在看清了公司的黑暗后，决心打爆全公司并离职！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>------[特色]------</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >痛打心智混乱的同事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同部门总是发生荒谬事件，辞职的人不得不用拳头与无法沟通的人们交流，拿我的公事包来吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/f1c2c6330fac08d666a1d85e5cae9fbd.poster.avif?t=1735374971\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/f1c2c6330fac08d666a1d85e5cae9fbd.webm?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/f1c2c6330fac08d666a1d85e5cae9fbd.mp4?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >职场里随机的技能抉择与资源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在职场历练中，你可以自由选择的技能流派，善用随机取得的资源效益最大化，你就是职场达人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/e58a0d0dad15cdeb9100cddace26dd79.poster.avif?t=1735374971\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/e58a0d0dad15cdeb9100cddace26dd79.webm?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/e58a0d0dad15cdeb9100cddace26dd79.mp4?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >友情为职场带来爱、勇气与希望</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职场黑暗中也会遇到如同朝阳的伙伴，战斗中可以呼叫他们登场支援，在伙伴的办公室还可以提升作战能力或改善公司劳动环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/3ceac543c02be498576f9b7f43a128f4.poster.avif?t=1735374971\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/3ceac543c02be498576f9b7f43a128f4.webm?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858450/extras/3ceac543c02be498576f9b7f43a128f4.mp4?t=1735374971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
